          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex> be a category; then the type of <fr:link href="jms-0082.xml" title="The Karoubi envelope" addr="jms-0082" type="local">Karoubi envelopes</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C\to  \widetilde {C}]]></fr:tex> for <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex> is contractible.</fr:p>
